cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.CR 

This paper deals with data repairing, which is a subfield of databases (cs.DB). The proposed method involves discovering rules automatically using similarity matching, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of algorithms for inconsistency resolution and data repairing, which are topics in data structures (cs.DS) and cryptography (cs.CR).
